---
// Componente para mostrar las promociones especiales con CIP
---

<section
  class="relative py-20 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-blue-50"
>
  <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/4 left-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300/10 to-blue-300/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300/10 to-blue-300/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Título de la sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-100 rounded-full text-blue-700 font-medium text-sm mb-6 border border-blue-200"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-5 w-5 mr-2"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 8v13m0-13V6a2 2 0 112 0v1.5m0 0l2.5 2.5M12 19l-2.5-2.5"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Promociones Especiales
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        <span
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >Certificado CIP</span
        >
        <br />
        <span class="text-gray-800">Colegio de Ingenieros del Perú</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Combina tu paquete con el prestigioso certificado del Colegio de
        Ingenieros del Perú y obtén beneficios adicionales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de promociones -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Promoción Paquete General + CIP -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
      >
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-4 w-4 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Promoción Especial
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            PAQUETE GENERAL + CIP
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 mb-4">
            <!-- <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-500 line-through"
              >S/ 50</span
            > -->
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-blue-600">S/ 40</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-blue-700 font-semibold mb-3">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Beneficio Exclusivo:</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-blue-600">
            <strong
              >¡Certificado de asistencia de la organización SIN COSTO
              ADICIONAL!</strong
            >
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Todo lo del Paquete General</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Certificado CIP oficial</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-green-700 font-semibold">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>            <span>+ Certificado de asistencia GRATIS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeRKLntstbofjfjgkCXhglaxathDv58uOBx3TueVtfXArz_vQ/viewform"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center"
        >
          Seleccionar Promoción
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Promoción Paquete Innova + CIP -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-xl border-2 border-blue-200 p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 relative"
      >
        <!-- Badge de mejor valor -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
          >
            🎯 Mejor Valor
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mb-6 mt-4">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-4 w-4 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Promoción Premium
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
            PAQUETE INNOVA + CIP
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 mb-4">
            <!-- <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-500 line-through"
              >S/ 55</span
            > -->
            <span class="text-4xl font-black text-blue-600">S/ 45</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center text-blue-700 font-semibold mb-3">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Beneficio Exclusivo:</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-blue-600">
            <strong>¡2 tickets ADICIONALES para sorteos del evento!</strong>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Todo lo del Paquete Innova</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Certificado CIP oficial</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-blue-700 font-semibold">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>+ 2 tickets extra para sorteos</span>
          </div>          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Total: 7 tickets para sorteos</div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeRKLntstbofjfjgkCXhglaxathDv58uOBx3TueVtfXArz_vQ/viewform"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center"
        >
          Seleccionar Promoción
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Información importante sobre el CIP -->
    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-600 mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-3">
            Información Importante sobre el Certificado CIP
          </h4>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-amber-700">
            <p>
              • El certificado del CIP tiene un <strong>costo de S/ 30</strong> y
              se gestiona directamente con el CIP el día del evento.
            </p>
            <p>
              • El pago se realiza <strong>exclusivamente con ellos</strong>, no
              con la organización del evento.
            </p>
            <p>
              • Este certificado es emitido por el <strong
                >Colegio de Ingenieros del Perú</strong
              > y tiene validez oficial.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
